{
  "stem": "19111.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In between the streets where it ended, they put brick walls up, and they enclosed everything.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And all the population was so crowded we had to share two families into one little room.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's how crowded it was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we had to-- those that came in first were able to find a better spot.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Those that came in from farther distances [INAUDIBLE] some people couldn't find a place.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had to stay on the stairs, and in the hallways, and on top of the bundles.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not really.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I couldn't remember the address because we were there a short time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I just want to mention this to you, that the people have-- by the time the ghettos were established, out of 65,000 people, 25,000 were already slaughtered in Ponary.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They're talking about around 30,000 to 35,000 people that actually moved into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My father and us, we came into the ghetto, and even though we were in the ghetto then, he still had to go to work.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The Germans gave him special permission.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They give him a special-- they called it a [INAUDIBLE] or a-- a certificate of employment.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Him and the other furriers had to continue to go to the fur factory and do the work while we were-- remained waiting for him.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He used to be marched back and forth in the morning to the factory and in the evening come back.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the Germans had discovered that it is too cumbersome for the furriers to keep marching back and forth like that, and so they obtained permission to form a small camp, a labor camp, outside of the ghetto, like three miles-- two or three miles away from the ghetto near the factory, and it was called Kailis.",
      "word_count": 57
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Actually, the factory was also Kailis.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
